                  <prov.body>
                    <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">1</label>
                      <para>
                        <text>In setting, varying, or revoking reasonable conditions under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 25(2)</citation></changeable>, the local authority or other body or person having jurisdiction over the road concerned may consider all or any of the following matters:</text>
                        <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">a</label>
