                      </para>
                    </subprov>
                    <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">3</label>
                      <para>
                        <text>However, a condition requiring the gas operator to increase amenity values<insertwords amend.level1="insert-unanimous"> (rather than merely maintaining them)</insertwords> may be imposed only if the part of the road on which the work is situated is within an area specifically identified in a long-term council community plan (as described in section 93 of the Local Government Act 2002) as being an area whose amenity values are to be protected or enhanced.</text>
